# TIPTAP VPS MCP mapping

This workspace folder is **TAPTAP_sauth** (TIPTAP South Africa). Use the VPS MCP servers listed for this project only.

## This project uses

| MCP server name (exact) | Host / domain | Use for |
|-------------------------|---------------|---------|
| **TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA** | `139.59.151.111` — `tiptapafrica.co.za` | Laravel app: deploy, Docker, nginx, `.env`, `php artisan`, queue, MySQL |
| **TIPTAP SOUTH BOT** | `167.71.44.10` — `wbot.tiptapafrica.co.za` | WhatsApp bot only (`TAPTAP-BOT` / `tiptopbot` Node Docker). **Not** Laravel. |

### Architecture (TAPTAP_sauth)

```
Meta WhatsApp  →  Laravel (TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA)  →  Bot (TIPTAP SOUTH BOT)
                 tiptapafrica.co.za                  wbot.tiptapafrica.co.za
```

- Laravel webhook: `https://tiptapafrica.co.za/api/whatsapp/webhook`
- Bot notify URL: `https://wbot.tiptapafrica.co.za/notify`
- Bot repo on VPS: `/opt/tiptap-sauth-bot/tiptopbot` (from `TAPTAP-BOT` GitHub)

When the user asks to deploy **WhatsApp bot for SA / sauth**, use MCP **`TIPTAP SOUTH BOT`** only.
When the user asks to deploy **Laravel / site / dashboard**, use MCP **`TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA`** only.

## Do not use for TAPTAP_sauth (unless user explicitly names another project)

| MCP server | Belongs to |
|------------|------------|
| **TITAPtz bot** | `TAPTAP tz` — TZ WhatsApp bot (`wa-notify.tiptapafrica.co.tz`) |
| **TIPTAP Saloon** | `Saloon ver` — Saloon Laravel app |

Never deploy SA Laravel to bot VPS, or TZ bot config to SA bot VPS.

## How to invoke

Use `CallMcpTool` with `server` set to the exact MCP name. Read the tool schema under the MCP descriptors before calling.

## Region note

- Country/market: South Africa (ZA)
- Do not confuse with **TAPTAP TZ** (Tanzania) or **Saloon ver**
